The paper deals with a natural language processing task of summarization, specifically for mathematical content. This falls under the sub-category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of pointer mechanism and multi-head attention mechanism suggests the use of machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
